ukuhlangana okuphelele: Uchungechunge olungapheli kuthiwa luhlangana ngokuphelele uma isamba samanani aphelele wezifinyezo sinomkhawulo
inani eliphelele: Inani elingelona elenegethivu lenombolo yangempela ngaphandle kokubheka uphawu lwayo
uchungechunge olushintshanayo: Uchungechunge olungapheli amagama awo ashintshana phakathi kokuphozithivu nokubi
ukuhlolwa kochungechunge olushintshayo: Indlela esetshenziswa ukufakazela ukuthi uchungechunge olushintshayo olunamagama ehla ngenani eliphelele luwuchungechunge oluguqukayo.
annulus: Into emise okwendandatho, isifunda esiboshwe yizindilinga ezimbili ezigxilile
i-antiderivative: Umsebenzi ohlukanisekayo okuphuma kwawo kulingana nomsebenzi wangempela
asymptote: Umugqa othi ibanga eliphakathi kwejika nomugqa lisondele kuziro njengokukodwa noma kokubili kwezixhumanisi zika-x noma y kuvame ukungapheli
indawo engaphansi kwejika: Okubalulekile okumelela indawo ephakathi kwekhevu y=f(x), i-eksisi x, kanye nemigqa eqondile x=a kanye no-x=b, lapho u-a no-b kuyimikhawulo yokuhlanganisa.
umthetho weketanga: Okuphuma kokunye komsebenzi oyinhlanganisela kuwukuphuma komsebenzi wangaphandle ohlaziywa ngezikhathi zokusebenza zangaphakathi okuphuma kokunye kokunye komsebenzi ongaphakathi.
umehluko wokubala: Ihlola izinga lokushintsha amanani. Isibalo sokuphuma kokunye sisetshenziselwa ukuchaza izinga loshintsho lomsebenzi
okuguquguqukayo okuzimele: Inani elikhohliswa kumsebenzi noma isibalo, ngokuvamile elimelela imbangela kubudlelwano bembangela-nomphumela
okuguquguqukayo okuncike: Umphumela noma umphumela kumsebenzi noma ubudlelwano obushintshayo ngokusekelwe kumanani amanye amanani
isizinda: Isho wonke amanani angenzeka angasetshenziswa njengokufakwayo kumsebenzi
ububanzi: Isethi yakho konke okuphumayo okungaba khona umsebenzi ongakhiqiza
umkhawulo: Umqondo ochaza ukuthi yimaphi amanani okukhiphayo umsebenzi osondela kuwo njengoba okokufaka kusondela kunani elithile
okuphuma kokunye: Umqondo okala izinga elisheshayo loshintsho noma ukuthambekela komugqa we-tangent endaweni ethile kumsebenzi
I-calculus ebalulekile: Isandiso sokubala esifaka phakathi ukuthola isinqamuleli sokuphuma kokunye komsebenzi okuphuma kokunye okukhitshwayo
indawo ebalulekile: Ukwenziwa ngokujwayelekile kokuhlanganisa okuhlukene ekuhlanganisweni phezu kwendawo
i-multivariable calculus: Isandiso se-calculus kokuguquguquka okukodwa kuya ku-calculus nemisebenzi yeziguquguquki ezimbalwa
i-vector calculus: Isandiso sokubala esiphathelene nokuhlukaniswa nokuhlanganiswa kwenkundla ye-vector endaweni ye-Euclidean enezinhlangothi ezintathu.
amandla e-vector: Inkambu ye-vector enikeza inkambu ye-solenoidal ngokusebenzisa i-curl opharetha
